    <briefdescription>
<para>Simple logger with optional file output. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>By default, logs to stdout. Call <ref refid="classemulator_1_1Logger_1aba19a95b86ae8bfa650c7b3453641e1a" kindref="member">set_file()</ref> to redirect output to a log file. Each message is prefixed with a timestamp and log level.</para>
<sect1 id="classemulator_1_1Logger_1autotoc_md16_1s1"><sect2 id="classemulator_1_1Logger_1autotoc_md16">
